					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85113223" rend="visible">
						<summary>A fragmentary collection of responses by Solomon ibn Adret.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85113223">
							<locus from="1r" to="162v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Responses</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">שאלות ותשובות </title>
							<note>
								<p>The manuscript concludes with no. 344.</p>
								<p>On folios 31-35 additional responses on Dine mamonot have been written in the margin by a later hand.</p>
							</note>
							<author>
								<persName xml:lang="en" key="http://viaf.org/viaf/27494766">Adret, Solomon ben Abraham, 1235-1310</persName>
								<persName xml:lang="he" key="http://viaf.org/viaf/27494766">אדרת, שלמה בן אברהם אבן (רשב"א)</persName>
							</author>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Paper codex of the 15th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="chart">
								<extent>162 folios <dimensions unit="mm" type="leaf">
										<height>270</height>
										<width>210</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>185</height>
										<width>120</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>162 folios (+ 3 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and 4 at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires of 6 to 8 leaves each.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Water-damaged, especially lower margins. Stained.</p>
									<p>Ink eating through pages.</p>
									<p>A leaf missing after folio 38.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="28 51" writtenLines="28 51">
									<p>Non-uniform layout. </p>
									<p>Hard-point ruling visible at times.</p>
									<p>Initial words in each section are given in larger characters.</p>
									<p>Some marginal notes and additions are present.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
						<handDesc hands="1">
							<summary>Sefardi semi-cursive scripts of the 15th century. </summary>
							<handNote script="Hebrew" scope="sole"/>
						</handDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Former owner's note, folio 1r.</p>
						</additions>
						<bindingDesc>
							<binding>
								<p>BM in-house.</p>
								<p>Spine title: 'Solomon ibn Adereth. Teshuboth. Hebrew. Brit. Mus. Additional 26,950.'</p>
							</binding>
						</bindingDesc>
